Package tuition

Class NonResident

java.lang.Object
tuition.Student
tuition.NonResident
Direct Known Subclasses:
International, TriState
public class NonResident extends Student
This class is derived from Student class and contains operations on NonResident students. It allows calculation of tuition due for students.
Author:
Ria Shah, Christian Bermudez
